    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though there are some minor stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear passenger door consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and all features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully functional. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, well-cared-for vehicle.",
