    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained cabin, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen that mirrors its original showroom state, offering both mechanical perfection and aesthetic distinction for the discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
